elements.name: Validate Agent Commission Maintenance in Launch Environment

steps.name: Run Test for "ebhlaunch" on Browser "chrome" and Enter the url for EBH
Login to the Agents Portal with username "SMRITIDHUNGANA" and password "Legendary@1"
Navigate to the Corporate Page on Main Menu and to the Settlements page
Navigate to the Agent Commission Maintenance page
Popup Menu arises insert password "ecomat"
Click on ok btn
Enter Agent/Location Code as "YNN" and click
Validate Agent Code Description and Agent is active

Validate Assert Values On Agent Commission Maintenance with Database Record "ebhlaunch" and "[EBHLaunch].[dbo].[usp_GetAgentCommissionDetails]" "YNN" "DCC Daily Chas Chrg DCC RESIDUAL" "BR BROKER COMMISSION BR ALL SPLIT" "YARD Yard Pull YARD NET"

arguments.val: DCC Daily Chas Chrg DCC RESIDUAL
BR BROKER COMMISSION BR ALL SPLIT

elements.name: Validate Agent Commission Calculation in Launch Environment

steps.name: Run Test for "ebhlaunch" on Browser "chrome" and Enter the url for EBH
Login to the Agents Portal with username "SMRITIDHUNGANA" and password "Legendary@1"
Navigate to the Corporate Page on Main Menu and to the Settlements page
Navigate to Agent Commission Calculation
Validate you are on Agent Commission Calculation page
Enter Pro Number as "CVA193110"
Click on Calculate Commission
Validate Vendor Code and Total Commission
Validate the records returned on Agent Commission Calculation with Database Record "ebhlaunch" and "[EBHLaunch].[dbo].[usp_GetAgentCommissionFinal]" "CVA" "193110"
Click on Display Matrix
Popup Menu arises insert password "ecomat"
Click on Ok button
Validate Primary Vendor Name and Primary Vendor Code
Close all open Browsers

elements.name: Validate Account File in Launch Environment

steps.name: Run Test for "ebhlaunch" on Browser "chrome" and Enter the url for EBH Basic File Maintenance
Login to the Agents Portal with username "SMRITIDHUNGANA" and password "Legendary@1" for EBH Basic File Maintenance
Navigate to the Corporate Page on Main Menu and to the Basic File Maintenance page for EBH Basic File Maintenance
Navigate to the Account File page
Enter Agent/Location Code as "BAY" in Search In Box and click
Verify Bill-To is Checked on and get the Records Returned for "BAY"
Validate Records Returned on Bill-To with Database Record "ebhlaunch" and "[EBHLaunch].[dbo].[ACCOUNTS]" "BAY %" "BAY METAL INC"
Click on SH/CON, Verify SH/CON is Checked on and get the Records Returned for "BAY"
Validate Records Returned on SH/CON with Database Record "ebhlaunch" and "[EBHLaunch].[dbo].[ACCOUNTS]" "BAY %" "BJW00632"
Click Select of first column
Validate Table Header and Name on Account File Maintenance
Close all open Browsers on EBH
